title: Increasing Your Capacity To Receive | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Increasing Your Capacity To Receive | Joel Osteen
description:
If you want to reach your full potential, you have to start expecting God’s favor. Don’t let limited thinking keep you from all that He wants to do in your life. 


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
